commentable_entity.ask: Johnny Depp as Mera in Aquaman 2
commentable_entity.title: Johnny Depp as Mera in Aquaman 2
commentable_entity.description:
With the Petition for Amber Heard to be removed from her role as "Mera" in the Movie "Aquaman 2" reaching 4 million signers, I officially petition DC Comics to instead:

  1. Have Johnny Depp play the Role of Mera
  2. Have Johnny Depp dress in the likeness of a certain Captain whose role is now unfulfilled.
  3. Have Johnny Depp act in the likeness of a certain Captain whose role is now unfulfilled. 
  4. Not change any aspect of the scrip to include, "Romantic and Physical" relationships to Jason Momoa (aquaman)
  5. Never reference the change by any script. 

If this petition hits 1 million signers, then I'll have someone word it better. 

If this petition hits 4 million people, DC Comics will have to do this, because... laws. 

If they do this... It will make more money than Shrek. 

God Teir. 

 

art credit by rebekah.fogle.arts
